# 🔐 Login Authentication System

**Intern:** Utkarsh  
**Task:** Level 2 — Task 4  
**File:** `Login.html`

## 📌 Overview
A complete login authentication system with Register, Login, and Secured Dashboard pages — built in pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## 🎯 Features
- ✅ User Registration with validation
- ✅ User Login — checks against registered accounts
- ✅ Secured Dashboard — only accessible after login
- ✅ Password strength meter
- ✅ Inline error messages
- ✅ Social login simulation (Google, GitHub)
- ✅ Toast notifications
- ✅ Logout functionality
- ✅ Demo account pre-loaded

## 🖥️ Tech Stack
| Technology | Usage |
|------------|-------|
| HTML5 | Multi-page structure |
| CSS3 | Glassmorphism UI, animations |
| JavaScript | Auth logic, validation, routing |

